{"tid":2369481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"博爾索納羅在特朗普落敗後改變立場　不再阻止華為參與5G建設","createTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T06:41:21.000Z","uid":159448,"like":4,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6976b2f7ee4ed36ec6912e3488b5e8de1fd1ae","tid":2369481,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"巴西聖保羅頁報（Folha de S&atilde;o Paulo）報道，總統博爾索納羅在美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）大選落敗後改變立場，不再阻止華為參與國內5G網絡建設。<br />\n<br />\n與特朗普相同，博爾索納羅曾以華為會與中國政府共享數據為由，拒絕華為參與國內5G網絡建設。在12月才有消息指出博爾索納羅正在尋找合法途徑，將華為排除在巴西的5G網絡之外。<br />\n<br />\n有分析指，由於中國是巴西最大貿易夥伴，華為亦有價格競爭優勢，博爾索納羅面臨政府和內部壓力，因此在特朗普確定敗選後改變立場。<br />\n<br />\n巴西副總統莫朗（Hamilton Mourao）表示，會讓所有尊重巴西主權及能提供數據保護保證的公司，參與該國5G建設。"},{"pid":"b38801413d4ace9ff8e1a597eda832eb4631bbd9","tid":2369481,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839efdfae03bbb495ab2678b079ec1d587ea829c","tid":2369481,"uid":17641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:33.000Z","msg":"狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8891c3c9d19fd1b43785aefb685592bcb9644fe","tid":2369481,"uid":40369,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"巴西不嬲都奶，見支製疫苗搵自己國民做白老鼠就知"},{"pid":"1e9cc6f923efb53b929437624beec1b5ea1797d9","tid":2369481,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"華為有無貨交先"},{"pid":"f8ac94f65bddd5723248b37c85818b892fd478d4","tid":2369481,"uid":127575,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:33:18.000Z","msg":"China Joe 做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59afddbb2acbb66069da9a4e4b41575e51bf3baa","tid":2369481,"uid":215